descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
Improve your wellness with Fun Fit Five, a unique app that combines Fitness and Meditation

# A Healthier You
- **Engage Your Whole Body**: Stay active with dynamic movements different Workout Types, go for stationary mode or raise bar with full 360º movement!

- **Calm your Soul:** Practice Meditation Sessions with breathing techniques. Try out a Cooldown Session right after your workouts, or configure your preferences in the Quick Meditation.

- **Keep your Streak:** Play everyday and every week to increase your Streaks.

[media]

# Features for you to take the First Step
- **Dynamic intensity:** Control the intensity of your workouts while you play at the click of a button.

- **Passthrough Mode:** Fitness in the real world, while merging with the virtual one.

- **Personalized for You:** Get recommendations tailored to your goals and preferences, making it easy to stay on track.

- **Ever-Growing Options:** Explore a wide variety of workouts, with new ones added regularly.

- **Track Your Progress:** View your history and see detailed stats about your accomplishments and stay connected to your improvement throughout your workout journey!

- **Share Your Feedback:** Rate the activities you’ve completed and contribute to the community by sharing your experience.
